  <Docs>
    <summary>A generic renderer interface.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>The renderer is responsible for making OpenGL calls to render a frame.</para>
      <para>
        <see cref="T:SkiaSharp.Views.Android.GLTextureView" /> clients typically create their own classes that implement this interface, and then call <see cref="M:SkiaSharp.Views.Android.GLTextureView.SetRenderer" /> to register the renderer with the <see cref="T:SkiaSharp.Views.Android.GLTextureView" />.</para>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
